      <title>Bob</title>
      <link>https://ar3ph.github.io/bob/</link>
      <pubDate>Mon, 05 Jan 2026 22:04:35 +0000</pubDate>
      <guid>https://ar3ph.github.io/bob/</guid>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;Idk if you have heard of &lt;a href=&#34;https://github.com/MordechaiHadad/bob&#34;&gt;&lt;code&gt;bob&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/a&gt;. It&amp;rsquo;s a version manager for neovim. For most people, the version of neovim does not matter. However, there are many a &lt;a href=&#34;https://github.com/vscode-neovim/vscode-neovim/issues/2238&#34;&gt;scenario&lt;/a&gt; where you may want the latest neovim on your system, and &lt;a href=&#34;https://github.com/MordechaiHadad/bob&#34;&gt;&lt;code&gt;bob&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/a&gt; is the thing you need.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;After you install &lt;code&gt;bob&lt;/code&gt;, here is a snippet to put the latest neovim in your &lt;code&gt;$PATH&lt;/code&gt;:&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;div class=&#34;highlight&#34;&gt;&lt;pre tabindex=&#34;0&#34; style=&#34;background-color:#f0f0f0;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;&#34;&gt;&lt;code class=&#34;language-bash&#34; data-lang=&#34;bash&#34;&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;white-space:pre;-webkit-user-select:none;user-select:none;margin-right:0.4em;padding:0 0.4em 0 0.4em;color:#7f7f7f&#34;&gt;1&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span&gt;bob use latest &lt;span style=&#34;color:#60a0b0;font-style:italic&#34;&gt;# downloads and installs neovim&lt;/span&gt;&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;white-space:pre;-webkit-user-select:none;user-select:none;margin-right:0.4em;padding:0 0.4em 0 0.4em;color:#7f7f7f&#34;&gt;2&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#007020&#34;&gt;export&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color:#bb60d5&#34;&gt;PATH&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#666&#34;&gt;=&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#4070a0&#34;&gt;&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#bb60d5&#34;&gt;$HOME&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#4070a0&#34;&gt;/.local/share/bob/nvim-bin:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#bb60d5&#34;&gt;$PATH&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#4070a0&#34;&gt;&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;white-space:pre;-webkit-user-select:none;user-select:none;margin-right:0.4em;padding:0 0.4em 0 0.4em;color:#7f7f7f&#34;&gt;3&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#007020&#34;&gt;echo&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color:#4070a0&#34;&gt;&amp;#39;export PATH=&amp;#34;$HOME/.local/share/bob/nvim-bin:$PATH&amp;#34;&amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt; &amp;gt;&amp;gt; ~/.zshrc&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</description>
